M|Assi|tx|\| New leads \| Head of mk \| Responsible for lead generation st \|
M|Assi|tx|\| On-time delivery \| Head of Operations \| Manages delivery team and processes \|
M|Assi|tx|\| Cash balance \| Head of fi \| Manages cash flow and collections \|
M|Assi|tx|\| Employee satisfaction \| Head of People/Integrator \| Responsible for culture and retention \|
M|Sett|Goal|
M|Sett|- **|** What have you averaged over the past 13 weeks?
M|Sett|- **|** What does the 1-Year Plan require?
M|Sett|- **|** What is realistically achievable w/ current resources?
M|Goal|tx|\| Metric \| 13-Week Average \| 1-Year Plan Requires \| Goal \|
M|Goal|tx|\|--------\|----------------\|---------------------\|------\|
M|Goal|tx|\| Weekly rv \| $42K \| $60K/week by Q4 \| $45K (Q1), $50K (Q2), $55K (Q3), $60K (Q4) \|
M|Goal|tx|\| New leads \| 80 \| 120/week \| 90 (Q1), 100 (Q2), 110 (Q3), 120 (Q4) \|
M|Goal|tx|\| Demos done \| 15 \| 25/week \| 18 (Q1), 20 (Q2), 22 (Q3), 25 (Q4) \|
M|Goal|tx|Goals can be updated quarterly during the Quarterly sn. Do not change them mid-quarter unless the business md fundamentally changes.
M|How |Each|
M|How |- **|** Number meets or exceeds the goal
M|How |- **|** Number misses the goal
M|How |When|
M|How |1. *|** The issue is understood and a correction is underway
M|How |2. *|** The issue needs the team's input to solve
